# Sprint 5 Implementation Plan: Finance, Notes, and Dashboard

Building the core management features: Finance (Payments), Clinical Documentation (Notes), and an informative Dashboard.

## Proposed Changes

---

### Backend Components

#### [MODIFY] [finance module]
- `PaymentService`: CRUD operations for payments.
- `PaymentController`: API endpoints for recording and listing payments. Access allowed for ADMIN, ASSISTANT, and ACCOUNTANT.
- Logic to calculate total balance for a patient.
- Exporting financial data functionality.

#### [NEW] [clinical-note module]
- [ClinicalNoteService](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/backend/src/modules/clinical-note/clinical-note.service.ts#4-42): CRUD operations for medical notes, prescriptions, and diagnoses.
- [ClinicalNoteController](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/backend/src/modules/clinical-note/clinical-note.controller.ts#10-38): API endpoints for managing notes.
- Visibility logic (DOCTOR_ONLY, STAFF, ALL).

#### [NEW] [dashboard module]
- [DashboardService](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/backend/src/modules/dashboard/dashboard.service.ts#5-68): Aggregates stats from [Patient](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/lib/api.ts#55-75), [Appointment](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/lib/api.ts#100-118), and [Payment](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/lib/api.ts#119-131) models.
- [DashboardController](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/backend/src/modules/dashboard/dashboard.controller.ts#8-21): Returns summary data for the clinic staff.

